window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Some forget why she was called the Queen Bitch.<br> <br> Not Anymore.<br> <br> Bethany Anne is going stir crazy after more than a decade of having to be 'The Empress.' Now, her advisors have to deal with an Empress who is determined to be on the front line.<br> <br> The Ixtali's come to the Etheric Empire, hat in hand.<br> <br> Nathan decides that the best way to handle soft intelligence, is to create a new company. What they name the new company should give a clue what it is about.<br> <br> The Skaine are able to finally get Ranger Tabitha's group right were their missiles can attack. The problem is, who is sucking whom into a trap?<br> <br> Strap back in, because Bethany Anne is putting the Queen's crown back on.<br> <br> Performed by Colleen Delany, Emily Beresford, Amanda Forstrom, Rayner Gabriel, Bradley Foster Smith, Nora Achrati, Eric Messner, Terence Aselford, Karen Novak, Michael John Casey, James Konicek, Ken Jackson, Drew Kopas, Steve Wannall, Emlyn McFarland, Christopher Williams, Scott McCormick, Richard Rohan, Christopher Walker, Yenni Ann, Joey Sourlis, Danny Gavigan, Su Ling Chan, Daniel Llaca, Tyler Hyrchuk, Sarah Ruth Thomas, Bianca Bryan, Zeke Alton, Jonathan Lee Taylor, Christopher Graybill, Anthony Palmini, Ryan Carlo Dalusung, Matthew Bassett, Lise Bruneau, Tony Nam, Keval Shah, Damon Alums, Michael Glenn, Marni Penning, James Lewis, David Cui Cui, Mort Shelby, Julie-Ann Elliott, Steve Wannall, Ren Kasey, Shanta Parasuraman, Eva Wilhelm, and Mort Shelby.</p>"; 
